_sText:
This is my first Deathrun map. All of the traps, triggers, sounds and textures should work. If the textures look goofy, take these three steps:
1. In console, type sv_cheats 1
2. In console, type mat_reloadallmaterials
3. In console, type sv_cheats 0

if that doesn't work, do it over again.
I tried my best to base the map off of the Half-Life 2 town of Ravenholm, which was hard.
I hope you like it!
